name: Ext_R5_ValueSet_co_property
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.ValueSet.compose.property for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version extension represents ValueSet.compose.property from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ValueSet|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B.

element.short: Property to return if client doesn't override
element.definition: A property to return in the expansion, if the client doesn't ask for any particular properties. May be either a code from the code system definition (convenient) or a the formal URI that refers to the property. The special value '*' means all properties known to the server.
element.comment: `ValueSet.compose.property` has no related element in R4B:ValueSet
